Quote: Since the pig was introduced by Captain Cook .. [fn] Hence modern Newzealand slang a <i>Captain Cook</i> or <i>Captain Cooker</i>, for a wild pig. (Current since the late 19th century.) Also, slang, <i>Pig-islands</i>, Newzealand, <i>Pig-islander</i>, a Newzealander.
